  <!--
      Segmented angular location-pin (no bullseye) in a neon purple -> pink linear gradient.
      Each polygon from the SVG has been converted to a <path> with the same coordinates.
      The gradient is defined inline using aapt:attr so Android Studio will render it correctly.
  -->

  <!-- Gradient definition (applied per-path via aapt:attr) -->
  <!-- We'll reuse the same gradient for every path so the overall object appears as a single blended shape. -->

  <!-- Upper-left segment -->
